You could use unique ids on your components to determine event ownership.

``` html
<div class="myComponent" data-guid="tweet-123456"></div>
```

IDs are server side generated in a [deterministic way](http://code.logos.com/blog/2011/04/generating_a_deterministic_guid.html) (eg. type-id)
The UI component gets the responseData (containing the ID) from the data component.

``` javascript
this.consumeData = function (event, data) {
   if (!data.GUID || data.GUID != this.$node.attr("data-guid")) {
      return;
   }
};
```

